title: The whispers of the high places
description: The whispers of the high places call to you, seeker. Ascend to Mountain Peak, where the very air thins with ancient energies. There, where the world unfolds beneath your feet, you must attempt 20 burpees. Only through this crucible of effort will the path forward be revealed.

trailLocation.title: Mountain Peak
trailLocation.description: A majestic mountain peak offering breathtaking views and challenging outdoor adventures.
